// @test regression/unused-vars-switch-expression
// @description Variables used only inside switch arms (condition or result) must not be reported as unused. analyzeExpression had no SwitchExpression case, so discriminant and case expressions were invisible. See plan/31 Finding 3.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects warnings: 0
//@version=6
indicator("x")
color bullColor = color.green
color bearColor = color.red
trendColor = switch
    close > open => bullColor
    => bearColor
plot(close, color = trendColor)
